  "texts": [
    "Firstly, we test the influence of the skill category on the assessment score.",
    "The ANOVA shows that the skill category has a significant effect on the assessment score (F(1, 101) = 92.6, p < 0.001): The assessment score for scientific skills (b) of ChatGPT is significantly higher than for skills beyond scientific knowledge (c).",
    "Secondly, testing the null hypothesis for the influence of the educational level on the assessment score results in a p-value of less than 0.01 (F(2, 202) = 5.29).",
    "This test indicates that the educational level significantly influences the assessment score.",
    "The answers for a lower educational level, for instance, the Bachelor level, are rated significantly better than for a higher educational level."
